data.description:
** NEW PRICE!  Home is vacant and ready for new owners to enjoy!  

A cozy 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with an open layout, master en-suite with a walk in closet.  The kitchen has stainless steele appliances, breakfast bar and a large pantry.  Roof 2018, AC & Water heater 2017.  2 Car Garage has pull down stairs for attic storage.  

You will enjoy the open air Florida room with water views and an outdoor patio to BBQ and watch the family of ducks. There  is also a fenced side yard for growing your favorite veggies or flowers.

Quiet community with no through traffic and low HOA dues ($383 per YEAR) beautiful community pool, playground and fishing pier.   

Great location and close to restaurants, schools, shopping and an easy drive to the beautiful beaches only 15 mins away
